item.description: Practice! Practice! Practice! Got your Roll? Don't lose it over the winter! Kayak Ways will be offering practice sessions all winter on lots of Sundays! We offer instruction in the shallow end and do a demo at 5pm for folks taking lessons, we encourage watching, its a great refresher! Arrive early and be ready for 5pm. Please bring clean kayaks! Most nights we will be eating out somewhere afterwards, all are invited to join us!
item.how_to_find_us: The Pool entrance is around the left side of the building in the back.
item.name: Biddeford Y Pool Rolling Practice
